{"tid":1111770,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一個累全家！傳黃心穎參演劇集被抽起","createTime":"2019-04-17T05:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T06:16:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c6049715310206d3c9c2aa000529738c8d4e09b2","tid":1111770,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"無綫小花黃心穎爆出與人夫許志安的偷食事件後，兩位主角遭全城圍剿，許志安全面停工開記招道歉並宣布全面停工，而黃心穎亦自食惡果，除了被傳遭無綫急急掟入雪櫃，全面暫停所有工作外，更「一個累全家」，連帶其有份參演的劇集均被抽起，見街遙遙無期！有消息指劇集《堅離地愛堅離地》本已排期於今年5至6月播出，惟主演之一的黃心穎突然捲入醜聞，因此無綫決定抽起劇集，改上由楊明及高海寧主演的《婚姻合伙人》。該劇的男、女主角張振朗及龔嘉欣無辜被牽連，網民紛紛到二人的社交網留言表示替他們感到不值。據知原本有不少客戶都有意找黃心穎拍廣告及洽談商演，現時亦急急打退堂鼓！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190417/photo/bkn-20190417123006283-0417_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190417125632\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190417%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190417123006283-0417_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190417125632&h=a06b955d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190417/bkn-20190417123006283-0417_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190417%2Fbkn-20190417123006283-0417_00862_001.html&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=f750ee48\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190417/bkn-20190417123006283-0417_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cbccb12ee852d94889c04ebcd9cb0f5c06183149","tid":1111770,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵兩張最醜嘅相"},{"pid":"2e9e1e542c491b90f2cbb591f1c08df23fe7f86a","tid":1111770,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T05:12:48.000Z","msg":"共加欣咁肉酸零演技做主角？"},{"pid":"bc056fd82812c03d99e317e262e5887cdaa72513","tid":1111770,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e9e1e542c491b90